        <h2>The Social Pillar</h2>
        <p>Social sustainability has had considerably less attention when compared to its other counter
            parts
            (economic
            and environmental sustainability).</p>
        <p>However it is still a topic of great importance that can affect everyones lives since it can
            be
            directly
            related to our individual lifestyle, ethical consumerism
            and means of transportation as well as range into other topics such as social equity,
            community
            development,
            human rights and responsibility as both individuals and
            organizations. Some of which will now be spoken in much more detail.</p>
