        <p><b>Ethical consumerism:</b> As being filled with wants and needs it is important to
            have some
            ethics
            about what and how much of it can or should be consumed.</p>
        <p>Some products can be harmfull to our well-being as well as the planet's either it be
            due to
            excessive
            intake of limited natural resources or harmful substances creatd in the process of
            it.</p>
        <br />
        <p><b>Community development:</b> A process where community members come together to take
            collective
            action
            and generate solutions to common problems. </p>
        <p>It can also be understood as professional discipline that is seen as a practice which
            promotes a
            sustainable development as well as equality by
            having such focus on exchange of information and opinions, about certain concepts,
            issues or
            projects
            which aim to enhance our social outcome.</p>
