        <p><b>Health equity:</b> Defends that no man or woman should ever be deprived from any of the
            three
            social
            determinants of health which are wealth, power and prestige
            since individuals who have been constantly deprived of such have shwon to have significant
            disadvantages
            from
            health inequities and tend to face worse
            health related outcomes in general than those who can acess such resources. Heath inequities
            stem from
            a
            failure
            in this distribution and not providing each individual with the resources he or she needs.
        </p>
